## ğŸš« Never Do
- Don't start with desktop design
- Don't use touch targets smaller than 44x44px on mobile
- Don't create horizontal scroll
- Don't hide important content on mobile
- Don't use hover effects as only interaction method
- Don't use font-weight 800 or 900
- Don't hardcode colors (use design tokens)
- Don't break 8px grid system
- Don't skip hover/focus states
- Don't compromise accessibility
- Don't change functionality during design updates

