## ğŸ“± Mobile Testing Checklist
Before deploying ANY design change:
- [ ] Test on iPhone SE (375px width - minimum)
- [ ] Test on iPhone 12/13/14 (390px width)
- [ ] Test on Galaxy S21 (360px width)
- [ ] Test on iPad (768px width)
- [ ] Test on iPad Pro (1024px width)
- [ ] Test portrait and landscape modes
- [ ] Test with iOS Safari (not just Chrome)
- [ ] Test touch interactions (tap, swipe, scroll)
- [ ] Test with slow 3G network
- [ ] Verify no horizontal scroll
- [ ] Verify all buttons are tappable (44x44px min)
- [ ] Verify modals work on small screens
- [ ] Verify forms are usable on mobile keyboard
- [ ] Test font sizes are readable without zoom

